IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: NCMEC CYBERTIP 173646681 ACTION TAKEN: On September 12, 2023, Cpl. Heid began an investigation into NCMEC Cybertip 173646681. The tip was reported by Facebook about one of its users uploading child pornography to their site. Facebook provided the following suspect information: Name: Andre Canty Date of Birth: 05-16-1992 Approximate Age: 31 Email Address: cantyandre510@gmail.com (Verified) Screen/User Name: andre.canty.961 ESP User ID: 100026088798324 Profile URL: https://www.facebook.com/andre.canty.961 IP Address: 73.250.110.160 (Login) 09-05-2023 23:28:16 UTC IP Address: 73.250.110.160 (Other) 09-05-2023 23:28:16 UTC IP Address: 73.250.110.160 (Other) 09-05-2023 23:27:14 UTC IP Address: 2601:145:c380:1140:e5b3:a461:4399:609 (Other) 08-31-2023 00:56:48 UTC IP Address: 2600:381:c190:14b0:75c2:4284:1881:99fa (Other) 08-21-2023 19:21:02 UTC IP Address: 2600:381:c190:14b0:75c2:4284:1881:99fa (Other) 08-21-2023 19:19:32 UTC IP Address: 72.94.212.91 (Other) 08-18-2023 23:34:31 UTC Facebook further provided the Upload IP address of the child pornography as 73.250.110.160. An open source check of the IP address showed the IP address came back to Comcast with a geo-location of Elkton, Maryland. Cpl Heid viewed the 2 videos which both depict child pornography. The descriptions are as follows: 1. Filename: YWNatrNQSBMcl8lA355841041_7141459332537803_3629633862362391216_n.mp4. This two minute and twenty-second video depicts what appears to be an adult black male sodomizing a black male child before ejaculating in the childs anus. The child is seen bent over from behind but does not appear to be fully developed. 2. Filename: TqMHjPBmWq53xce8373438661_6539214289477966_6776583736602411645_n.mp4. This is a one minute and fifth one-second video depicts a young white/hispanic female reasonably believed to be 8-10 years of age. The child is nude on her back while being vaginally penetrated by what appears to be an adult male. Cpl. Heid sent a subpoena request to Comcast for the listed IP address through the Howard County States Attorneys Office. Cpl. Heid will be awaiting its return before any additional investigation. The case remains open at this time. CASE OPEN
